'''You Came, You Saw, We Co-Oped''' is an [[achievement]] set in the category ''[[Meetings in Outrealm: Series I]]''. The achievements are earned by completing [[Domains]] with other players in [[Co-Op Mode]].

==Achievements==
{{Achievements by Category Table|You Came, You Saw, We Co-Oped}}

==Trivia==
===Etymology===
*The English name is likely based on the phrase "I came, I saw, I conquered." The English phrase is a translation of the Latin phrase ''{{w|Veni, vidi, vici}}'', which is popularly attributed to Julius Caesar after his swift victory over the Kingdom of Pontus.
